{"tid":2512144,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一樣好尷尬嘅事","createTime":"2021-05-01T12:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T13:08:01.000Z","uid":40945,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9ab45b2272cd2516322576dbd83e7e68201305ef","tid":2512144,"uid":40945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:33:13.000Z","msg":"我講先...<br />\n<br />\n頭先去食飯，有班外國人係到<br />\n我同男朋友係到估佢地係講緊西班牙文定法文。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲開左google translate 用語音mode睇下佢地講緊咩文。<br />\n<br />\n我仲講： 好正呀，好似去左外國咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解d外國人走嘅時候，男朋友同佢地對望左，跟住d外國人係到同男朋友吹水。 <br />\n<br />\n其中一個人用廣東話話問我：d野好唔好食呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nOh no....<br />\n我地講嘅所有野都俾佢聽曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係講人壞話，但係我地喺到估佢地講緊咩話，咁八婆同咁白痴嘅內容就俾佢地聽曬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗚....<br />\n<br />\n男朋友話我諗多左，人地只係好nice 咁吹下水<br />\n<br />\n但我覺得佢係想同我地講，我識聽廣東話架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗚....我以後唔咁八啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51a7c72ba7f6aaf2d76e6347e2c69c98035a1c6","tid":2512144,"uid":156326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:34:12.000Z","msg":"jm9"},{"pid":"e914162bd64d71b0d96d320dba645fc8239b86ee","tid":2512144,"uid":307927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:35:40.000Z","msg":"都叫你班女人唔好咁八婆"},{"pid":"24ba518efa3ad3a05bd15b6cd7776ada62944670","tid":2512144,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:35:52.000Z","msg":"有男朋友既一律tldr"},{"pid":"bd17a37b49e6bbd4d8876831069afc3dcecb0533","tid":2512144,"uid":366655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:36:24.000Z","msg":"沖涼拍打J片流出咗畀連登仔笑賓周短<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4371ddaec6f38c7cd76e26969ef457ccca8d3d","tid":2512144,"uid":34926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:44:06.000Z","msg":"好尷尬咩"},{"pid":"98df379f5102876740efe613ad548239f9abe8f8","tid":2512144,"uid":40945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e914162bd64d71b0d96d320dba645fc8239b86ee","tid":2512144,"uid":307927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:35:40.000Z","msg":"都叫你班女人唔好咁八婆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好𤓓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333e1a1eb916c00c6d4322c77852e805d102ed7e","tid":2512144,"uid":40945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24ba518efa3ad3a05bd15b6cd7776ada62944670","tid":2512144,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:35:52.000Z","msg":"有男朋友既一律tldr"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fcbff3ef6cc0d43aec7993ebe634015fa02c457","tid":2512144,"uid":40945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd17a37b49e6bbd4d8876831069afc3dcecb0533","tid":2512144,"uid":366655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:36:24.000Z","msg":"沖涼拍打J片流出咗畀連登仔笑賓周短<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T12:49:17.000Z","msg":"真定假呀"},{"pid":"11fba01db325ed30ead71d1e490865ff17e14335","tid":2512144,"uid":40945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b4371ddaec6f38c7cd76e26969ef457ccca8d3d","tid":2512144,"uid":34926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep